                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "卡利贝尔",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "克洛达尔的私生子在灾变后成为了丘丘人，并陷入了昏迷状态。克洛达尔利用深渊的力量治疗他的儿子，并愿望他成为「",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 5747,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/17/59155606/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_8107650970862387032.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "命运的织机",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "坎瑞亚的「五大罪人」中的一位，唤回了卡利贝尔的神智，超然的存在。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "深渊教团",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "克洛达尔 · 亚尔伯里奇创始的组织，其主要目标是为了因神明灭国的坎瑞亚，覆灭七国，淹没神座。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "旅行者的血亲",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "受到克洛达尔的影响，最终成为深渊教团的「公主 / 王子殿下」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
